        <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Find Your Comeback Word</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">Enter your tiles into our word finder to discover your highest-scoring options — including bingo possibilities that could swing the game in a single turn.</p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">Try the Word Finder →</a>
      </div>

